fm_use: I(attendance * 100) ~ relative_age + I(relative_age^2) | grade +      year | 0 | mst_id
name: I(attendance*100)_parametric

fm_use: I(singleparent * 100) ~ relative_age + I(relative_age^2) | grade +      year | 0 | mst_id
name: I(singleparent*100)_parametric

fm_use: I(publicassistance * 100) ~ relative_age + I(relative_age^2) |      grade + year | 0 | mst_id
name: I(publicassistance*100)_parametric

name: I(attendance*100)_rdd

fm_use: I(singleparent * 100) ~ 1 + distance_cutoff + upper_cutoff +      distance_cutoff * upper_cutoff + as.factor(grade) + as.factor(year)
name: I(singleparent*100)_rdd

fm_use: I(publicassistance * 100) ~ 1 + distance_cutoff + upper_cutoff +      distance_cutoff * upper_cutoff + as.factor(grade) + as.factor(year)
name: I(publicassistance*100)_rdd
